<lb n="0040a25" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT51p0040a2501">梁鐘山延賢寺釋慧勝</item>
<lb n="0040a26" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT51p0040a2601">隋東都翻經館釋彥琮<note place="inline">常誦梵本</note></item>
